\n\r\nCan we have the de-referenced label exported instead of the id in **text classification**?\r\nCurrent:\r\n```\r\n{\"annotations\": [{\"label\": 1, \"user\": 1}]}\r\n```\r\nRequested:\r\n```\r\n{\"annotations\": [{\"label\": \"class_1\", \"user\": 1}]}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAs in sequence tagging we have\r\n```\r\n{\"labels\": [[26, 34, \"PER\"], [35, 56, \"LOC\"]]}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI do aware that we could export the label to get the ID mapping, but the problem is that we could only upload 1 MB at max so that we need to separate it into a few projects.\r\nThe ID mapping in the new project would be different and it is troublesome to keep track.\r\nSo I don't think ID mapping is the solution.\r\n\r\nThank you in advance.","closed_by":{"login":"icoxfog417","id":544269,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU0NDI2OQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/544269?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417","html_url":"https://github.com/icoxfog417","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icoxfog417/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/issues/749/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/issues/749/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}